# Handout local environment configuration.
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the sections you need.
# .env.local is gitignored. Re-run `scripts/setup.sh` any time for a
# refresher on what the values mean and where to obtain them.
#
# All sections are optional unless noted.

# === Section: Bot identity (optional) ===
# A GitHub App that gives Claude a separate identity for commits and PRs
# made from this devcontainer. Skip this section to have Claude operate
# under your own GitHub user identity instead.
CLAUDEBOT_APP_ID=
CLAUDEBOT_INSTALLATION_ID=
CLAUDEBOT_PRIVATE_KEY_PATH=.gh-app-private-key.pem
